quests.desc: Welcome to another fast paced round of TextWorld! First step, travel south. Then, pick up the key that's in the cellar. And then, move north. And then, travel east. With that accomplished, unlock the safe in the lounge with the key. Then, open the safe. And then, retrieve the rectangular latchkey from the safe. Then, doublecheck that the rectangular locker is unlocked. Then, ensure that the rectangular locker is open. After that, pick up the latchkey from the rectangular locker inside the lounge. Got that? Good!

objective: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First, it would be great if you could travel south. With that over with, pick up the key in the cellar. And then, go to the north. And then, venture east. Once you get through with that, check that the safe inside the lounge is unlocked with the key. Then, ensure that the safe is open. And then, take the rectangular latchkey from the safe inside the lounge. Then, look and see that the rectangular locker within the lounge is unlocked. After that, make sure that the rectangular locker is wide open. And then, retrieve the latchkey from the rectangular locker in the lounge. Once that's all handled, you can stop!
